      public static Parser createSACParser() throws DOMException
      Create a SAC Parser specified by the system property org.w3c.css.sac.parser.

      By default, uses this library's SAC Parser.

      Returns:
      the SAC parser.
      Throws:
      DOMException - INVALID_ACCESS_ERR if the Parser could not be instantiated.
